e d'Or nominated movie 'Mountains May Depart' directed by Jia Zhang-Ke in 2015. He later starred the lead role Zhu Chaoyang in iQiyi's original drama \"The Secret Corner\".","name":"Rong Zishan","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"榮梓杉","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Жун Цзы Шань","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"榮梓杉，2006 年 2 月 3 日出生，中國內地影視演員、平面模特。現居江蘇蘇州。愛好籃球、遊泳、繪畫等。2015 年，因飾演賈樟柯電影《山河故人》中童年張到樂一角為觀眾所熟知。\n\n代表作：電影《山河故人》、 《秘果》、 《西小河的夏天》；網劇《最好的我們》；電視劇《旋風少女第二季》、《軍師聯盟》、《如懿傳》等。","name":"榮梓杉","primary":false}}]}},"person_120351_translations":{"at":1773688736680,"data":{"id":120351,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Ken Mitsuishi (光石 研 Mitsuishi Ken, born 26 September 1961) is a Japanese actor. He has appeared in films such as Chaos and Tokyo Playboy Club.","name":"Ken Mitsuishi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"光石研，日本男演员，福冈县北九州市出身。","name":"光石研","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"光石研","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"光石研","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"미츠이시 켄","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ken Micuiši","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ken Mitsuishi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","na